---
// Bitemporal timeline visualization
// Shows two timelines (system time and business time) with fact events and query range highlights
---

<div class="timeline-container">
  <div class="timeline-title">Bitemporal Data Model</div>
  <div class="timeline-explanation">
    Every fact in SpectraDB lives in two time dimensions: <strong>system time</strong> (when it was recorded)
    and <strong>business time</strong> (when it was true in the real world).
  </div>

  <div class="timeline-diagram">
    <!-- System Time Axis -->
    <div class="timeline-section">
      <div class="timeline-axis-title">System Time (commit_ts)</div>
      <div class="timeline-axis">
        <div class="timeline-track">
          <div class="timeline-event" style="left: 10%">
            <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
            <div class="timeline-event-label">v1 written<br/><small>ts=100</small></div>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-event" style="left: 35%">
            <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
            <div class="timeline-event-label">v2 correction<br/><small>ts=200</small></div>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-event" style="left: 60%">
            <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
            <div class="timeline-event-label">v3 update<br/><small>ts=350</small></div>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-event" style="left: 85%">
            <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
            <div class="timeline-event-label">v4 latest<br/><small>ts=500</small></div>
          </div>

          <!-- AS OF query range -->
          <div class="timeline-query-highlight" style="left: 0; width: 42%">
            <div class="timeline-query-label">AS OF 250</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-axis-labels">
          <span>ts=0</span>
          <span>ts=250</span>
          <span>ts=500</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="timeline-note">
        <code>AS OF 250</code> returns v2 — the latest version visible at commit timestamp 250.
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Business Time Axis -->
    <div class="timeline-section">
      <div class="timeline-axis-title">Business Time (valid_from → valid_to)</div>
      <div class="timeline-axis">
        <div class="timeline-track">
          <!-- Business time ranges as bars -->
          <div class="timeline-range" style="left: 5%; width: 30%">
            <div class="timeline-range-bar rate1"></div>
            <div class="timeline-range-label">Rate 3.5%<br/><small>Jan–Mar 2024</small></div>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-range" style="left: 35%; width: 25%">
            <div class="timeline-range-bar rate2"></div>
            <div class="timeline-range-label">Rate 4.0%<br/><small>Apr–Jun 2024</small></div>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-range" style="left: 60%; width: 35%">
            <div class="timeline-range-bar rate3"></div>
            <div class="timeline-range-label">Rate 4.25%<br/><small>Jul–Dec 2024</small></div>
          </div>

          <!-- VALID AT marker -->
          <div class="timeline-valid-marker" style="left: 50%">
            <div class="timeline-valid-line"></div>
            <div class="timeline-valid-label">VALID AT May 2024</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-axis-labels">
          <span>Jan 2024</span>
          <span>Jul 2024</span>
          <span>Dec 2024</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="timeline-note">
        <code>VALID AT 1715000000</code> (May 2024) returns Rate 4.0% — the fact valid at that business time.
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="timeline-combined">
    <div class="timeline-combined-title">Combined: AS OF + VALID AT</div>
    <div class="timeline-combined-desc">
      Combine both dimensions: <code>SELECT rate FROM policies AS OF 200 VALID AT 1715000000</code>
      <br/>
      This returns the rate that <em>was known at system time 200</em> and <em>was valid in May 2024</em>.
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .timeline-container {
    padding: 1.5rem 0;
  }
  .timeline-title {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--sl-color-white);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .timeline-explanation {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--sl-color-gray-3);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .timeline-explanation strong {
    color: var(--spectra-blue);
  }
  .timeline-diagram {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2.5rem;
  }
  .timeline-section {
    background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.5);
    border: 1px solid var(--spectra-card-border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
  }
  .timeline-axis-title {
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--spectra-violet);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.03em;
  }
  .timeline-axis {
    position: relative;
  }
  .timeline-track {
    position: relative;
    height: 80px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--spectra-card-border), var(--spectra-card-border));
    background-size: 100% 2px;
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
    background-position: center;
  }
  .timeline-event {
    position: absolute;
    top: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(-50%);
    text-align: center;
  }
  .timeline-dot {
    width: 14px;
    height: 14px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--spectra-gradient);
    margin: 0 auto;
    animation: pulse-dot 2s ease-in-out infinite;
    box-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.4);
  }
  @keyframes pulse-dot {
    0%, 100% { box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.4); }
    50% { box-shadow: 0 0 0 8px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0); }
  }
  .timeline-event-label {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    color: var(--sl-color-gray-3);
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .timeline-event-label small {
    color: var(--sl-color-gray-4);
  }
  .timeline-query-highlight {
    position: absolute;
    top: -8px;
    height: calc(100% + 16px);
    background: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.08);
    border-right: 2px dashed var(--spectra-blue);
    border-radius: 4px;
  }
  .timeline-query-label {
    position: absolute;
    top: -20px;
    right: -8px;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--spectra-blue);
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .timeline-axis-labels {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    color: var(--sl-color-gray-4);
  }
  .timeline-range {
    position: absolute;
    top: 50%;
    transform: translateY(-50%);
    text-align: center;
  }
  .timeline-range-bar {
    height: 24px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    opacity: 0.8;
  }
  .timeline-range-bar.rate1 { background: var(--spectra-blue); }
  .timeline-range-bar.rate2 { background: var(--spectra-violet); }
  .timeline-range-bar.rate3 { background: var(--spectra-emerald); }
  .timeline-range-label {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    color: var(--sl-color-gray-3);
    margin-top: 0.3rem;
  }
  .timeline-range-label small {
    color: var(--sl-color-gray-4);
  }
  .timeline-valid-marker {
    position: absolute;
    top: -12px;
    height: calc(100% + 24px);
    transform: translateX(-50%);
  }
  .timeline-valid-line {
    width: 2px;
    height: 100%;
    background: var(--spectra-amber);
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .timeline-valid-label {
    position: absolute;
    top: -20px;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--spectra-amber);
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .timeline-note {
    margin-top: 1rem;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--sl-color-gray-3);
    line-height: 1.5;
    padding: 0.75rem;
    background: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.05);
    border-radius: 8px;
    border-left: 3px solid var(--spectra-blue);
  }
  .timeline-note code {
    color: var(--spectra-blue);
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  .timeline-combined {
    margin-top: 2rem;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    background: rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.05);
    border: 1px solid rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.2);
    border-radius: 12px;
  }
  .timeline-combined-title {
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--spectra-violet);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .timeline-combined-desc {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--sl-color-gray-3);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  .timeline-combined-desc code {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--spectra-blue);
  }
  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .timeline-event-label { font-size: 0.6rem; }
    .timeline-range-label { font-size: 0.6rem; }
  }
</style>
